Four-population test was executed in TreeMix to verify the derived introgression events. The f4 (A, B; C, D) was calculated as described in Reich et al. (2009) [30], and its standard error (SE) was estimated using a Block Jackknife procedure with a block size of 100,000 SNPs. To assess significance of introgression, Z-score was calculated as \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
